Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\3c&HD831D9&\fad(450,450)\pos(1010,64)}-通向剧场之路-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.63,0:03:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES军第13输送部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要进行犯人押送 请求着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认紧急情况 许可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了 做这样恶趣味的伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真惨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在发源地秋叶星剧场观看公演是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这片天空的颜色到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择了心里上压抑的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让内心不被演艺迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以大家的眼神都那样没有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:03:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES那帮家伙做了多么恶劣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有WOTA入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.85,0:04:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里交战就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认为粉红色会很可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 Kojiharu姐 很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 小惠 还有76期的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Papa大厨 筹到食材了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些也可以吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的 含有丰富的维他命 还具有药效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.73,0:05:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个可以吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了小惠 可以吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再去弄点来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野生偶像 简称野偶的诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长 争气点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin 身体还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.75,0:05:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin 伤怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 只是头痛得有点厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易来到秋叶星 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找医生 认真治疗一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋叶星的人 憎恨着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.56,0:05:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为00抛弃了秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退是迫不得已的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了优子 那个时候只有撤退一条路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是之后城市立即遭到了占领
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DGTO的宣传充斥了人们的双耳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短短几天居然开始洗脑宣传了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能将天空的颜色传达到网络媒体上去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说这里到底是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是对于我们0048而言 极为神圣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时是连成员也禁止进入的圣域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.96,0:06:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从来了这里之后就觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听到什么声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么声音在身体的深处回响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin的Kirara…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 动作幅度再大一些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara完全没闪耀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话根本没法让双晶素产生反应的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做得更好才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再强烈一些 迅速一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意识到手指的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样 再这样一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样 像这样动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是不甘心全交给成员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己也想登场表演吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 现在的翼实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.67,0:07:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在已经做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 现在只能拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救秋叶星 拯救大家的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼姐哭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.23,0:08:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位都看到了吧 那就是翼的Kirara的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连毕业已久的翼 都能让Kirara发光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做到这点 就需要超越愿望 超越祈祷的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强烈的思念!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强烈的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些现役成员都做不到 还有何办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:20.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连翼这老太婆都豁出去拼命到这个地步了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老 老太婆?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 来拼一把
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别输给老太婆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连咪酱都这么毒舌啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 继续练习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的热情点燃了大家的心灵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼酱 GOOD JOB
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不相信她们的话就无从谈起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,强烈的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把秋叶星夺回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最珍贵的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得以实现的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使约定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得以实现的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形形色色的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,形形色色的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心怀着各种各样的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想却相同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成为0048
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被梦想所鞭策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们乘上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往秋叶星的 梦想列车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.30,0:10:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是 哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 应该是在上排练课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到站了 不过这是哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:10:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takamina姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:10:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开门了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是秋叶星!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个 没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.49,0:11:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接纳我们梦想的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara和双晶素产生反应了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定没错 有这种程度的反应的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好真的能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 做得太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙还没有醒过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙 凪沙!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.54,0:12:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理是怎么来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道 我 一直在一片黑暗里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在原地不动的话 总觉得会被那片黑暗碾碎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就开始跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定在那时可以忘记一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾见过这番景象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是不是有人在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.27,0:13:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧 还真有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.46,0:13:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不能再往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 第13代啊酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有第6代由依
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有其他的Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱她们在闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可那是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剧场？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是却像咫尺天涯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子她怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙 刚才那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你们看到的毫无疑问是AKB48剧场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AKB48开始于灭亡前的地球上的日本秋叶原的一个小剧场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里集合的少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踏出了梦想的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 地球不是已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大概不是真正的地球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是由强烈思念所形成的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 优子她并没有到达那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.91,0:15:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕优子她还并没有完全成为Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那个时候 优子放射出来的的确是Center Nova的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 而且也满足了Center Nova的产生条件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她没有满足Center Nova的消失条件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova的消失条件？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失的绝对条件是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越时空的可怕的一体感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越时空？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不单和成员 观众 工作人员还有会场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还同未来与过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法用语言表达的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一切融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得无处不在 无处可见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这带有丝丝恐怖的心醉神迷里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是优子的那消失方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却像是独自一人躲进孤独的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演唱会会场在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请排队等候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里真的合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合适 翼小姐来过联系了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让Flying get闯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在秋叶星被DES给重重包围
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本闯不进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信00等下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 夺回作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备超空间跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双晶素同步装置正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara驱动器也没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便跳跃成功了 也不知道会到什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舵就交给你来掌了 咪酱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK OK 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kojiharu Tomochin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也去会场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和演唱会那边会合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.85,0:17:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.46,0:17:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先圣老师的传话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin 难道你听得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 可并不是语言 而是身体直接感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次夺回秋叶星作战的关键就在于
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO NAME
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO NAME 无名的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细的我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在没时间去想它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 去准备演唱会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦闯了进去 就开始演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:18:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占领了秋叶星的DGTO绝对会给DES增援
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前 要把演唱会的气氛炒到最热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.00,0:18:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在蓝花星上的演唱会 我发不出声音的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮了我 可我现在却什么忙都帮不上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和爸爸的封闭之门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为我所渴望的都在那道门后面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道如果一直被黑暗吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就永远无法打开那道门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我一定要成为Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵达那道门的门后面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.53,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也为了夺回秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开那道门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能让智惠理的爸爸领会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居民们已经成功转移
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么万一的话 就由我们来抵挡DES
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快看天空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传送门？难道是00？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去会撞上去 咪酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天爷保佑我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剧场女神们成功降临了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AKB0048
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有脸回来 你们这些叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚回去 叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前明明那么善良的秋叶星居民
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs30}滚回去 滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不抓紧的话 会被DES袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要大家齐心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位想想特训的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种场合说要齐心协力…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:20:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋叶星的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深藏于人们内心深处的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也随着演唱会调动起来 相互联系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.47,0:21:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara和双晶素 假如能对此集体无意识产生反应的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了达到这点 观众们的感情十分重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.49,0:21:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.79,0:21:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅凭成员们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能使双晶素产生反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻里子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takamina姐 麻里子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论成员们怎么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法传达给人们的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楚方…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.69,0:21:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋叶星的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是那么善良
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的表情却那么可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.35,0:22:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.10,0:22:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不能就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚回去 滚回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:51.72,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}Ho！Ho！ Ho！ Ho！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:56.18,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}いつだって夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.47,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}遠くに見える
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:02.97,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}届かないくらい距離感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:05.17,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}足元の石を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.40,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ひとつ拾って
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.98,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}がむしゃらになって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:12.14,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}投げてみろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:16.04,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}君の目の前に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:18.31,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}川が流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:22.91,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}広く 大きな川だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:26.19,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}暗く深くても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:30.51,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}流れ速くても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:33.99,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}怯えなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:36.18,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:40.56,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}そうだ 向こう岸はある
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:49.13,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}もっと 自分を信じろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:52.52,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}River !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:54.63,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}AH - AH - AH - AH -
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.09,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}自分に言い訳するんじゃねぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:59.12,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}AH - AH - AH - AH -
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.70,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}やってみなけりゃわかんねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.60,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}AH - AH - AH - AH -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.99,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}まっすぐ進むしかねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.89,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ずっと ずっと ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.46,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}歩き続けろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:11.48,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}決めた道を !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:14.66,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}君の心にも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:17.96,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}川が流れる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:21.38,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}汗と涙の川だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.77,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}失敗してしまっても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:29.12,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}流されてしまっても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.65,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}やり直せばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:34.85,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}弱音吐くなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:39.00,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢にしがみつくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:46.69,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}願い 叶う日が来るまで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:47.60,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}川を渡れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:48.90,inj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}You can do it !
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:56.18,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.47,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}梦想总是远在天际
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.73,0:20:02.97,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}让人产生无法靠近的距离感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.25,0:20:05.17,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}将脚下的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:07.40,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}捡起一块
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.98,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不顾一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:12.14,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}将它投出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:16.04,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在你眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:18.31,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}河水在流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:22.91,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}宽广无际的河流
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:26.19,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使暗不见底
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:30.51,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使急流恶浪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:33.99,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不必害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:36.18,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使距离遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:40.56,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}也终将抵达彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:49.13,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}再对自己多些自信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:57.09,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不要对自己找藉口！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.70,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不试试看就不知道结果！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.99,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}只能勇往直前！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.89,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}一直 一直 一直
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:09.46,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}向前迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:11.48,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在自己定下的路上！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:14.66,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}你的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:17.96,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}河水也在流淌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:21.38,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}那是汗水与泪水的河流！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.77,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使失败
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:29.12,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}即使被激流卷走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:32.65,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}只要再试一次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:34.85,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不要说泄气话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:39.00,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}牢牢抓住梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:46.69,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}直到祈愿实现的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:47.60,inc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}渡过河流！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:28.00,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}いつかの願いは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:32.47,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}土の中で眠って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:41.75,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}約束の時刻に 希望の根が出るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:45.75,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}二人が出会った頃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:50.79,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢など まだだめだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:54.69,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}どれくらい時が過ぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:23:00.16,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}花は咲くのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:05.47,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}この涙を君に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:09.94,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}もっと君が輝くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:15.51,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}ずっと見守ってた沈默の空から
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:20.15,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}今 僕は雨になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:23.62,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}あぁ 君に捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.62,0:23:28.26,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}こんな僕に出来ることは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:33.36,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}キミの虚しさを少しでも癒すこと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:38.70,opedj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}さぁ 僕は雨になろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:28.00,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知何时的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:32.47,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}沉睡在土壤中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:41.75,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}在约定好的时间 萌生出希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:45.75,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}当两人相遇之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:50.79,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}梦想还不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:54.69,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}不知要过多长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.79,0:23:00.16,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}花才会绽放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.00,0:23:05.47,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}把这颗眼泪献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:09.94,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}如果你能够更加闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:15.51,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我会从一直看着你的沉默的天空中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.51,0:23:20.15,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}成雨落下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.52,0:23:23.62,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}啊 献给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.62,0:23:28.26,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}我所能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:33.36,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}就是轻轻抚慰空虚的你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:38.70,opedc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}来吧 我将成为雨
